NUMBERS AND MATH FUNCTIONS
->python can handle diff tyoes of numbers like int(+ve, -ve, 0), float(decimal nums), complex where complex nums are used for advanced math(2+3j etc)
* Python in-built Math functions:
x = -7
y = 3.14159
print(abs(x))        # 7 (absolute value)
print(round(y, 2))   # 3.14 (rounding)
print(pow(2, 3))     # 8 (2^3)
print(max(10, 20, 30))  # 30
print(min(10, 20, 30))  # 10
* python has Math library fro more adv functions:
import math
print(math.sqrt(16))     # 4.0
print(math.factorial(5)) # 120
print(math.ceil(3.4))    # 4 (round up)
print(math.floor(3.9))   # 3 (round down)
print(math.pi)           # 3.141592653589793
